Usage
-----

	termplot                                           \
		up1:'uptime | "awk { print \$8 }"'         \
		mem:'free | awk "/Mem:/ { print \$3 }"'    \
		wlan0:'iw dev wlan0 link | awk "/bitrate/ { print \$3 }"'


